title: Taylor Swift Sings 'Boom Clap' With Charli XCX in Toronto! (Video)
text: Taylor Swift rocks a brand new outfit alongside special guest Charli XCX on stage during the 1989 World Tour concert at Rogers Center on Saturday night (October 3) in Toronto, Canada.
